messages.subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] Digest Number 511
messages.msgSnippet: ... But where do we go if we want to sample some Carolina bbq but don t want to give this guy any money? Since I live in Memphis, I have to try it every where.
messages.messageBody:
>Piggie Park. Mary (Zenmomma) and Karin---you'll pass it as you come from the

>airport to the hotel on the right. Can't miss it! HUGE flag!
>

But where do we go if we want to sample some Carolina bbq but don't want
to give this guy any money?

Since I live in Memphis, I have to try it every where.


Sikes. Hammy's. Dukes (but it's not very good). Plenty of options!

Since you're driving through NC, I'd recommend some NC Q---vinegar-based and
delicious!

I'll point you in the right direction.

Kelly
